DOCKER_STARK_MODULE_SUBMODULE_SERVICE_PORTAINER_NAME=portainer
DOCKER_STARK_MODULE_SUBMODULE_SERVICE_PORTAINER_RELEASE=1.24.1


### DOCKER SERVICE IMAGE
